 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ea814a96bb35d35abbec06d3456bc17d147c51","tid":127340,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:57:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">__ __ __ __ , __ __ __ __ !</span></span>"},{"pid":"85b9db81823f163bb5c005eb5609ae40a137d073","tid":127340,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/22504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F22504.jpg&h=56b4e9d7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a30f469a16a41e16e756be3a940a54c1e5d352d","tid":127340,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:57:50.000Z","msg":"咁快就跪低，垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d40bc59674a19c109be0e9fb1794c5649e49cbb","tid":127340,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"跪係到叩頭認錯先"},{"pid":"70c9033ff807ece3e416df587f39a6f9865eee78","tid":127340,"uid":17759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/22504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.